      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Steve Maughan</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:152px;\"><a href=\"http://www.monarchchess.com/index.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/2/21/SteveMaughan.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:SteveMaughan.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Steve Maughan <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Steve Maughan</b>,<br />\na British <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management_consulting\">management consultant</a> residing in Florida <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nSteve Maughan is computer chess and <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> programmer, and author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engines <a href=\"/Monarch\" title=\"Monarch\">Monarch</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/Maverick\" title=\"Maverick\">Maverick</a>, and the Othello or Reversi program <i>Edge Reversi</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \nIn March 2013, Steve started  a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blog\">blog</a> on the development of his chess engine Maverick <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1999\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1999</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Maughan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Are You Sure It's Better?</i> <a href=\"/Selective_Search\" title=\"Selective Search\">Selective Search</a> 40, pp. 21, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesscomputeruk.com/SS_40.pdf\">pdf</a> hosted by <a href=\"/Mike_Watters\" title=\"Mike Watters\">Mike Watters</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Maughan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1999\">1999</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Maughan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1999\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=41612\">Hash Tables - Should one store EP, Castling rights etc?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 30, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Castling_Rights\" title=\"Castling Rights\">Castling Rights</a>, <a href=\"/En_passant\" title=\"En passant\">En passant</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Maughan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=112884\">A couple of Questions re ABDADA</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/ABDADA\" title=\"ABDADA\">ABDADA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=144854\">Alpha beta fail soft, pruning &amp; hash bounds?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a>, <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Bound\" title=\"Bound\">Bound</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Maughan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=2407&amp;p=11195\">Fruit's Board Representation?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 27, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\">Fruit</a>, <a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18864\">What's Strelka's Secret Sauce?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Strelka\" title=\"Strelka\">Strelka</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Maughan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46490\">Chess and the \"Golden Ratio\"...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 19, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46584\">A Computer Chess Google+ Community...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 26, 2012 <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47402\">*NEW* - ChessProgramming.net Blog...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 04, 2013 <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47615\">I'm Puzzled - Storing Piece Info &amp; Magic Move Gen...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47710\">How to Shift Left (by) a Negative Number??</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 05, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Pushes_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Pawn Pushes (Bitboards)\">Pawn Pushes (Bitboards)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48816\">First Release of Maverick Chess Engine!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 01, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48911\">Writing to a Text File (Thread Safe)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 10, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Logging\" title=\"Logging\">Logging</a>, <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50140\">New Computer Chess News Website (Easy for Authors!)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54345\">Free Version of Visual Studio Professional 2013!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 14, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Maughan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55578\">OT: Finding the Line of the Assert Fail?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 07, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Debugging\" title=\"Debugging\">Debugging</a> <a href=\"/Maverick\" title=\"Maverick\">Maverick</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56311\">Adding an Extension Results in Deeper General Search!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 10, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn_Extensions\" title=\"Passed Pawn Extensions\">Passed Pawn Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58031\">Lazy SMP Better than YBWC?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 23, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a>, <a href=\"/Young_Brothers_Wait_Concept\" title=\"Young Brothers Wait Concept\">Young Brothers Wait Concept</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66443\">Connect 4 AlphaZero implemented using Python...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 29, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero</a>, <a href=\"/Connect_Four\" title=\"Connect Four\">Connect Four</a>, <a href=\"/Python\" title=\"Python\">Python</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67432\">Ryzen 2 and BMI2?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 13, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/AMD\" title=\"AMD\">AMD</a>, <a href=\"/BMI2\" title=\"BMI2\">BMI2</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68054\">New WCCC Version of The Baron Released (Plus Polyglot Opening Book)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 23, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/WCCC_2018\" title=\"WCCC 2018\">WCCC 2018</a>, <a href=\"/The_Baron\" title=\"The Baron\">The Baron</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68458\">Fritz 13 SE?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 16, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Fritz\" title=\"Fritz\">Fritz</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</